data.description: Beat today's high rates with an Assumable 2.375% VA loan!!  Discover a blend of timeless elegance and modern sophistication in this stunning Puyallup residence. Nestled amidst a lush, manicured lawn, the home's exterior beckons with a grand facade, muted gray tones, and a welcoming wrap-around porch, perfect for leisurely evenings. Inside, a harmonious blend of space and light unfolds. Expansive windows and an open floor plan illuminate tasteful design choices from the gourmet kitchen to the sumptuous living spaces. With 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and two stories, there’s room for everyone to find their sanctuary. Includes Tesla hookup! Beyond the confines of this beautiful home, Puyallup offers a bounty of local amenities.
